{"tid":999193,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘不敗傳說 高雷屹立不倒","createTime":"2019-01-28T13:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:19:33.000Z","uid":161865,"like":175,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e081f3e46e2cbdc8b090eebd38524db2fafb136b","tid":999193,"uid":161865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:58:57.000Z","msg":"我哋高雷武鬥學院自古以嚟都站在眾生之上<br />\n乜嘢地理亞 伽藍 暮光<br />\n我哋一隻手指都捽撚死你哋<br />\n<br />\n我哋嘅校工個個都十八銅人出身<br />\n你估我唔想準時返學<br />\n只係每朝打唔贏佢哋都唔俾入學校<br />\n<br />\n每個老師都座底空手道黑帶八段<br />\n仲用摺櫈?<br />\n個個都好似拎住支光管當光劍<br />\n分分鐘勁過skywalker<br />\n<br />\n啲主任級就全部專業保鏢出身<br />\n以前奧巴馬想揾佢哋出山都俾佢哋拒絕哂<br />\n仲要全部師承胡力威師傅<br />\n好揪過葉問<br />\n<br />\n區區董之英想挑戰我哋地位<br />\n算撚數啦你<br />\n高雷永遠最強"},{"pid":"056f12f9fbcc59bb1915110c0914535e5d5732a3","tid":999193,"uid":51567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"迫不及待想玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27c09ddd81217540955524a50db12a09008a5fb","tid":999193,"uid":161865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"056f12f9fbcc59bb1915110c0914535e5d5732a3","tid":999193,"uid":51567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:00:16.000Z","msg":"迫不及待想玩玩了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:01:39.000Z","msg":"嚟挑機"},{"pid":"cab9dccb7534891d1b05396cc62d569f842709fb","tid":999193,"uid":41670,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"咪撚就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日就去董之英踢佢地館<br />\n高雷嘅學生開片起碼跟江湖規矩<br />\n董之英班垃圾根本淨係識圍威喂 欺凌人扮哂野咁<br />\n我電威式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6dc65d30e0be62755969da9033db7b5